description: Galactic Ordinals are a 300 manually created PFP collection paying homage to NFT culture and Bitcoin, self-inscribed via our own node, using only sats ending in 69 & 420 for the culture. Rising from the ashes of the Terra Collapse, Galactic Punks and The Galactic DAO are inspired by the crypto ecosystem, community and drive for innovation. Known for paving the way for Terra NFTs and helping to shape NFTs across the Cosmos ecosystems. All roads lead back to Bitcoin and we invite you, fren, to join us on the ride. Range: 17,910,245-17,910,904.
name: Galactic Ordinals
